{"tid":2385520,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IZ*ONE 大展銷量威力　登韓國女歌手 2020 銷量冠軍寶座！","createTime":"2021-01-29T05:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T06:39:17.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e3ef9b7a387babcf9bf734f966ef3cff815b0306","tid":2385520,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T05:45:29.000Z","msg":"自出道以來，IZ*ONE 就不斷展現強大的銷量威力，恭喜她們成為去年在韓國最暢銷的女性歌手！<br />\n<br />\n根據 Hanteo Chart 昨天公布的數據顯示，IZ*ONE 在整個 2020 年間共賣出了 1,292,919 張專輯，一舉拿下年度女歌手累積銷量的冠軍頭銜。<br />\n<br />\nIZ*ONE 去年從 2 月便開始展開積極的活動，發行了為出道企劃畫下句點的正規一輯〈BLOOM*IZ〉，熱銷 415,827 張；短短 4 個月後，她們又推出迷你三輯〈Oneiric Diary〉，以全新面貌再創佳績，賣出了439,994 張。<br />\n<br />\n最後，IZ*ONE 在年底前發行的迷你四輯〈One-reeler〉也賣出多達 378,443 張，構成一整年的亮眼成績！另一方面，IZ*ONE 的合約預定於今年 4 月到期，不過日前已傳出有望延長的消息。"},{"pid":"b948aad4091c13aff00efda177c9b88122aedbbc","tid":2385520,"uid":205928,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T05:46:18.000Z","msg":"勁過blackpink?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6e234c8375b4349e90b72258da569959f6afa3","tid":2385520,"uid":256796,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T05:47:07.000Z","msg":"永續吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6a5dc9ff221189cdc930d270e62fe7e9676c31","tid":2385520,"uid":261849,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T05:47:21.000Z","msg":"屌你樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ab69ef94048a968b1460fb20441471268ac0a77","tid":2385520,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b948aad4091c13aff00efda177c9b88122aedbbc","tid":2385520,"uid":205928,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyT